<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Prenatal_Care</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/IndexPage_P.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Prenatal_Care.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.2/css/all.min.css" />
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="max-width:100%; width:100%; margin: 0 auto; border-top: 4px blue;">
        <header>
            <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm border-bottom box-shadow mb-3" style="background-color: #32adfa;">
                @*---------------start of the Sidebar-------------------*@
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <div id="main">
                        <span style="font-size:30px;cursor:pointer;" onclick="openNav()">&#9776; menu</span>
                    </div>
                    <div id="mySidenav" class="sidenav">
                        <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="closebtn" onclick="closeNav()" style="border:none">&times;</a>
                        <div class="navbar-header">
                            @*  <img class="client" src="~/css/Miss N. Tmebani .jpg" alt="" style="align-content:center;"/> *@
                        </div>
                        <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Prenatal" asp-action="Index"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> &nbsp; Home</a>
                        @* <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Prenatal" asp-action="CheckUps"><i class="fas fa-calendar-week"></i> &nbsp; Check-Ups</a> *@
                        <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Prenatal" asp-action="PersonalInfo"><i class="fas fa-stream"></i> &nbsp; Personal Info</a>
                        <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Prenatal" asp-action="AboutUs"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> &nbsp; About Us</a>
                        <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Prenatal" asp-action="FeedBack"><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> &nbsp; Feedback</a>
                        <a class="" asp-area="" asp-controller="Staff" asp-action="Index"><i class="fas fa-calendar-week"></i> &nbsp; Stuff Portal</a>
                    </div>
                    @*------------------ Script for Opening and Closing the Side Bar ----------------------------*@
                    <script>
                        function openNav() {
                            document.getElementById("mySidenav").style.width = "325px";
                            document.getElementById("main").style.marginLeft = "325px";
                        }
                        function closeNav() {
                            document.getElementById("mySidenav").style.width = "0";
                            document.getElementById("main").style.marginLeft = "0";
                        }
                    </script>
                </div>
            </nav> @*--------------------- end of Sidebar --------------------*@
        </header>
    </div>
    <div class="background"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    @*-------------------Blog Section-------------------*@
    <section id="blog">
        @*--------------------Heading---------------------*@
        <div class="blog-heading">
            <span>Recent Posts</span>
            <h3>Prenatal News</h3>
        </div>

        @*-----------------------blog-container------------------------*@
        <div class="blog-container">
            @*-------------------box-1----------------------*@
            <div class="blog-box">
                @*--------img--------*@
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <img src="~/css/Card1.jpg" alt="News" />
                </div>
                @*----------text----------*@
                <div class="blog-text">
                    <span>15 Aug 2023 / By Dr. Priyom Bose, Ph.D.</span>
                    <a href="https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230815/Understanding-human-body-composition-in-the-first-two-years-of-life.aspx" class="blog-title">Understanding human body composition in the first two years of life</a>
                    <p>Historically, anthropometric measurements such as height, weight, and head circumference have been used to assess the development, growth, and nutritional status of infants. This stage of life is crucial in developing phenotypic metabolic profiles that are subsequently associated with health status later in life.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230815/Understanding-human-body-composition-in-the-first-two-years-of-life.aspx">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            @*-------------------box-2----------------------*@
            <div class="blog-box">
                @*--------img--------*@
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <img src="~/css/Card2.png" alt="News" />
                </div>
                @*----------text----------*@
                <div class="blog-text">
                    <span>16 Aug 2023 / By Miss Pooja Toshniwal Paharia</span>
                    <a href="https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230816/What-gestational-age-at-delivery-is-associated-with-the-best-perinatal-outcomes-in-term-singleton-pregnancies-conceived-with-infertility-treatment.aspx" class="blog-title">What gestational age at delivery is associated with the best perinatal outcomes in term singleton pregnancies conceived with infertility treatment?</a>
                    <p>Pregnancies conceived using infertility therapies face elevated perinatal risks, including stillbirths, perinatal mortality, and low birth weight.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230816/What-gestational-age-at-delivery-is-associated-with-the-best-perinatal-outcomes-in-term-singleton-pregnancies-conceived-with-infertility-treatment.aspx">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            @*-------------------box-3----------------------*@
            <div class="blog-box">
                @*--------img--------*@
                <div class="blog-img">
                    <img src="~/css/Card3.jpg" alt="News" />
                </div>
                @*----------text----------*@
                <div class="blog-text">
                    <span>17 May 2023 / By Miss Tanushree Banerjee</span>
                    <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/mothers-day-2023-should-women-get-pregnant-in-the-late-30s-experts-weigh-in/articleshow/100213164.cms" class="blog-title">Mother's Day 2023: Should women get pregnant in their late 30s? Experts weigh in</a>
                    <p>
                        From making bold career choices to embracing motherhood, women know when it is the right time for them to take the next step in their life.
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/mothers-day-2023-should-women-get-pregnant-in-the-late-30s-experts-weigh-in/articleshow/100213164.cms">Read More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>
</body>
</html>